  "text": "Lemma 2.4. [Alber [CITATION_1] ] Let E be a reflexive, strictly convex and smooth Banach space, let C be a nonempty closed convex subset of E and let x ∈ E. Then φ(y, Π c x) + φ(Π c x, x) ≤ φ(y, x) for all y ∈ C.",
